<a id="EditorExportPreset"></a>

# EditorExportPreset

**Inherits:** [RefCounted](RefCounted.md) **\<** [Object](Object.md)

Export preset configuration.

<!-- classref-introduction-group -->

## Description

Represents the configuration of an export preset, as created by the editor's export dialog. An **EditorExportPreset** instance is intended to be used a read-only configuration passed to the [EditorExportPlatform](EditorExportPlatform.md) methods when exporting the project.

## Method Descriptions

<a id="EditorExportPreset_method_are_advanced_options_enabled"></a>

<!-- classref-method -->

[bool](bool.md) **are_advanced_options_enabled**\ (\ ) <span class="const">const</span> [ðŸ”—](#EditorExportPreset_method_are_advanced_options_enabled)

Returns ``true`` if the "Advanced" toggle is enabled in the export dialog.

<hr class="classref-item-separator"/>

<a id="EditorExportPreset_method_get_custom_features"></a>

<!-- classref-method -->

[String](String.md) **get_custom_features**\ (\ ) <span class="const">const</span> [ðŸ”—](#EditorExportPreset_method_get_custom_features)

Returns a comma-separated list of custom features added to this preset, as a string. See [Feature tags](../tutorials/export/feature_tags.md) in the documentation for more information.

<hr class="classref-item-separator"/>

<a id="EditorExportPreset_method_get_customized_files"></a>

<!-- classref-method -->

[Dictionary](Dictionary.md) **get_customized_files**\ (\ ) <span class="const">const</span> [ðŸ”—](#EditorExportPreset_method_get_customized_files)

Returns a dictionary of files selected in the "Resources" tab of the export dialog. The dictionary's keys are file paths, and its values are the corresponding export modes: ``"strip"``, ``"keep"``, or ``"remove"``. See also [get_file_export_mode()](EditorExportPreset.md#EditorExportPreset_method_get_file_export_mode).

<hr class="classref-item-separator"/>

<!-- classref-method -->

Returns the export mode used by GDScript files. ``0`` for "Text", ``1`` for "Binary tokens", and ``2`` for "Compressed binary tokens (smaller files)".

<a id="EditorExportPreset_method_get_version"></a>

<!-- classref-method -->

[String](String.md) **get_version**\ (\ name\: [StringName](StringName.md), windows_version\: [bool](bool.md)\ ) <span class="const">const</span> [ðŸ”—](#EditorExportPreset_method_get_version)

Returns the preset's version number, or fall back to the [ProjectSettings.application/config/version](ProjectSettings.md#ProjectSettings_property_application/config/version) project setting if set to an empty string.

If `windows_version` is ``true``, formats the returned version number to be compatible with Windows executable metadata.
